dct_title_s: Western Australia state map / Hema Maps ; cartography, Ray Martin.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights and shading. Map of Greater Hobart showing: roads; railroads; walking, hiking, and biking routes; topology; political divisions and localities; national parks; and rest areas, fueling stations, and campgrounds. Includes index to towns and communities, legend, and text. Panel title. Includes on verso 10 ancillary national park maps, colored illustrations with accompanying text, a listing of national parks, their tourist facilities and contact details, and a shared legend for the national parks maps. Map is waterproof.
dct_publisher_sm: Eight Mile Plains, Qld. : Hema Maps, ©2019.
